All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.accessibility.Accessible, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable
public class ExitPanel
extends RightPanel

Class ExitPanel represents a confirm-close dialog. It has fixed size of 480 x 480 pixel and is located as rightPanel in the MainPanel. You can add a YesNoListener to recieve events, if one of the buttons is clicked.

Version:
1.0
